ServerBarrier.scala: a simple implementation of a barrier using a server.

BarrierTest.scala: a test for a Barrier.

PrefixSums.scala: the prefix sums example.

PrefixSumsTest.scala: tester for the prefix sums examlpe (and also the
corresponding exercise).

Jacobi.scala: Jacobian iteration.

Jacobitest.scala: test of Jacobi.scala.

JacobiExperiment.scala: experiment comparing the different implementations of
Jacobian iteration.

BFSGraphSearch.scala: strict breadth-first search, using a barrier
synchronisation at the end of each round.

Exercises
=========

ServerCombiningBarrier.scala: a combining barrier.

BarrierLog.scala: barrier synchronisation in O(log n) time.

PrefixSumsShared.scala: prefix sums using shared variables.

ArrayMax.scala: finding the maximum in an array.

Smooth.scala: base for the image smoothing problem, and a sequential program
(distribution).

SmoothShared.scala: concurrent image smoothing program.

SmoothSharedTest.scala: test program for the previous (distribution).

LargestComponent.scala: code for the largest component problem.